{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"552e92f3d2","title":"对谭震林关于国务院农口几个单位情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"394e042a45","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":30,"articleId":"552e92f3d2"}],"tags":[{"id":"89f0012853","name":"谭震林","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"ffead2e3d2","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"552e92f3d2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"谭震林，当时任中共中央政治局委员、国务院副总理兼农林办公室主任。"},{"id":"6dd6dfe9fe","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"552e92f3d2","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林彪，在中共八届十一中全会上继续当选为中央政治局常委，不久被称中央副主席。恩来，即周思来。"},{"id":"e3158733eb","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"552e92f3d2","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指谭震林1967年1月28日给毛泽东等并中央文化革命小组的报告。报告对农垦部、农业部、水产部等单位开展文化大革命的情况，谈了自已的看法，表明了自己的态度。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f27a09df37","type":"title","text":"对谭震林关于国务院农口几个单位情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"552e92f3d2"},{"id":"ffead2e3d2","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪、恩来同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"552e92f3d2"},{"id":"6dd6dfe9fe","type":"paragraph","text":"此件值得一阅。党、政、军、民、学、工厂、农村、商业内部，都混入了少数反革命分子、右派分子、变质分子。此次运动中这些人大部都自己跳了出来，是大好事。应由革命群众认真查明彻底批倒，然后分别轻重，韵情处理。请你们注意这个问题。谭震林的意见是正确的。此件请周印发较多的同志看，引起警惕","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"552e92f3d2"},{"id":"e3158733eb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"552e92f3d2"},{"id":"3f8a63fcc7","type":"paragraph","text":"一月册日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"552e92f3d2"}],"page":{"id